            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-300 mb-6 italic">
            "Jan has a special gift: he listens attentively, asks precise questions, and skillfully draws crucial conclusions - all in an incredibly calm manner. What particularly stands out is his technical depth combined with pronounced entrepreneurial thinking and genuine practical experience."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-charcoal-700 pt-4">
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-stone-100">Dieter Sartorius</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">CEO, EAN50 GmbH</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
