          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-300 mb-6 italic">
            "Working with Jan has brought much clarity and focus to our marketing strategy. With Jan, you can really tell that he has incredible experience. And I'm grateful that we were able to benefit from it."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-charcoal-700 pt-4">
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-stone-100">Jörg Kundrath</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">Founder & CEO, MINDSET MOVERS</p>
          </div>
        </div>

